Package: libra-setup
Version: 1.0-1
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Riley Hernandez <riley@caldo.tech>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Depends: libssl3
Description: Installs the Libra service (big-brother).
 This package installs the big-brother binary and configures it to run
 as a systemd service. It also creates a dedicated system user and sets
 up udev rules required for Phidgets USB devices.
